text: A video shared on Facebook purportedly shows a member of a Maasai tribe in Kenya whipping people who violate the country’s curfew during the coronavirus pandemic.
entity_strings: Facebook, Kenya, Maasai tribe, coronavirus pandemic

text: A video shows a member of the Maasai tribe whipping people in Kenya who refused to obey the government's self-quarantine orders during the COVID-19 pandemic.
A video shared on Facebook purportedly shows Zimbabwean police beating churchgoers for violating the country’s ban on large gatherings during the coronavirus pandemic.
